"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7535928\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2><span style=\"color:null;\">Information about the table:</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"color:null;\"><u><strong style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">This information is provided for the convenience of the public and does not constitute endorsement, recommendation, or favoring by the National Park Service.</strong></u></span><br/>\n<br/>\n<strong>The companies listed below hold a valid Grand Canyon National Park CUA effective January 1, 2026 - December 2026. Not all CUA Holders requested to be listed on the CUA Public Directory. </strong><br/>\n<br/>\n<span style=\"color:null;\">The table listed on this page is a sortable table.These companies opted to be posted on the website. </span></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7904994\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7904994\"> \n<div class=\"SortableDataset\">\n<h2 class=\"SortableDataset__Heading\">Bicycle Tour Companies</h2>\n\n<table class=\"display nowrap\" id=\"sortable_E5B45607-9A2D-3567-2FB9C606494F6228\" style=\"width:100%;\" summary=\"Companies that provide tours by bicycle.\">\n<caption class=\"hide-text\">Bicycle Tour Companies</caption><thead><tr>\n<th scope=\"col\">Company</th>\n<th scope=\"col\">Website</th>\n<th scope=\"col\">Email</th>\n<th scope=\"col\">Phone</th>\n<th scope=\"col\">Pick Up Locations</th>\n</tr></thead></table>\n\n<p class=\"SortableDataset__DownloadLink\"><a download=\"\" href=\"/common/uploads/sortable_dataset/grca/E5B45607-9A2D-3567-2FB9C606494F6228/grca-Bicycle.csv?t=1774883323894\">Download This Dataset</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7904993\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7904993\">\n<div class=\"SortableDataset\">\n<h2 class=\"SortableDataset__Heading\">Motorcycle Tour Companies</h2>\n\n<table class=\"display nowrap\" id=\"sortable_E5AC86F4-D2A9-AF0B-C1E28BFBD418EFFC\" style=\"width:100%;\" summary=\"Companies that provide Motorcycle Tours\">\n<caption class=\"hide-text\">Motorcycle Tour Companies</caption><thead><tr>\n<th scope=\"col\">Company</th>\n<th scope=\"col\">Website</th>\n<th scope=\"col\">Email</th>\n<th scope=\"col\">Phone</th>\n<th scope=\"col\">Pick Up Locations</th>\n</tr></thead></table>\n\n<p class=\"SortableDataset__DownloadLink\"><a download=\"\" href=\"/common/uploads/sortable_dataset/grca/E5AC86F4-D2A9-AF0B-C1E28BFBD418EFFC/grca-Motorcycle.csv?t=1774883324144\">Download This Dataset</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_7904522\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_7904522\">\n<div class=\"Component ListingGrid -large\">\n<div class=\"ListingGrid-header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\">Related Links</h2>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"row\">\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/getinvolved/rb_cualist.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/getinvolved/rb_cualist.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Multiple vehicles at the entrance station\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/F9A3111D-C1C5-B987-986BCEEA54EBBEDC.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/F9A3111D-C1C5-B987-986BCEEA54EBBEDC.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nRoadbased Tours and Transportation CUAs\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#navigate_next\"></use>\n</svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">Link to CUA lists for companies that operate inside Grand Canyon National Park for Road Based and Transportation Services. </p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/calendar.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/planyourvisit/calendar.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A group of park visitors listening to a ranger talk. The ranger is on the right and smiling.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/1F633A3C-1DD8-B71B-0B261C3FE60B9054.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/1F633A3C-1DD8-B71B-0B261C3FE60B9054.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nSouth Rim: Programs and Special Events\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#navigate_next\"></use>\n</svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">Here's the schedule of this week's ranger and astronomy programs, cultural demonstrations and special events. </p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/getinvolved/cua.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/getinvolved/cua.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Two large tour buses and two transit vans are parked in a loading zone.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/B9CD5943-968A-1B6D-F459FC087BEFD371.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/B9CD5943-968A-1B6D-F459FC087BEFD371.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nCommercial Use Authorization (CUA)\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#navigate_next\"></use>\n</svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">CUAs are required for road-based tours, guided backcountry trips and all other commercial activities for visitors within the park.</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/getinvolved/cua-list.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/getinvolved/cua-list.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"Canyon View\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/BBA26047-A4FE-8D06-D3B18ED2B906E168.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/BBA26047-A4FE-8D06-D3B18ED2B906E168.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<span class=\"ActivityListing-subtitle\">Back to CUA List</span>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nCUA Public Directory\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#navigate_next\"></use>\n</svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">CUA Public Directory lists are located here for authorized companies that opted to be posted on the Grand Canyon Website. </p>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: March 25, 2026</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n <!-- ParkFooter -->\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div><!-- end of <div main> -->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!-- the rest of the scripts are leftovers from before the centennial down and should be pared down where possible -->\n\n<link href=\"/common/commonspot/templates/assets/libs/colorbox/colorbox.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n<div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"outdated-browser\" role=\"dialog\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n</div>\n</body>",
